The existing PXE and server provisioning setup is a combination of
manual and automated steps. It is explained in the docs.
Eventually all of it will be automated.

pxelinux.cfg = This folder contains the different PXE config files.
               The files are named per server role.
kickstart = this folder contains the CentOS Anaconda installer kickstart files.
            The files are name per server role.
nfs = content thats accessed from NFS share by the kickstart scripts
